## Rules

1. **Token-first components**
   - Every property (color, padding, radius) must come from tokens.

2. **Component states**
   - Always define: default, hover, active, focus, disabled.

3. **Example: Button**
   ```css
   .button-primary {
     background: var(--surface-primary-default);
     color: var(--text-inverse);
     padding: var(--spacing-sm) var(--spacing-md);
     border-radius: var(--radius-md);
   }
   .button-primary:hover {
     background: var(--surface-primary-hover);
   }
   .button-primary:disabled {
     background: var(--surface-neutral-disabled);
     color: var(--text-neutral-disabled);
   }
